(1972) Next album = }} 'Indweller' is the fifth and last studio album by the English group Quintessence. Dave Codling and Shiva Shankar Jones have left the group. The result are more acoustic and melodic songs, without the energy that Shiva's voice and Dave's electric guitar gave to the compositions.
